{
  "stem": "7600.5",
  "chunk_idx": 17,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I said, if you don't go away this minute, I'll scream.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he went out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So then I talked to this other man who was also there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I said, what happened?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He said, well, you can't stay here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I said, I know I can't stay here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because he maybe is going to get worse.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So he said, I'll, I'll cover for you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Can go look for-- there were lots of hotels there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So I took to-- made the rounds.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I found a little family hotel where the people came during the, during the summer.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they had children.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I became a children's waitress.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They, they ate separately in separate rooms and separate things.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK, so I was--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then when the summer ended, I went back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I went back to, to waitressing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then I finally had made arrange-- you know, though Betty, I met some other people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they had some organizations there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And somebody always, you know, always gave out information of where you could find a job.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then somebody said, you know, there's a new, new something is coming here in Belgium.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And by that time, he had taken over Belgium.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Hitler had taken over Belgium and France-- that when I was in the Catskills, I remember we all cried when we saw a picture of the Nazis marching down the Arc de Triomphe.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We all cried.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then he had taken over Belgium.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he said all the Belgian diamond-- the diamond business is coming over here.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there is a place down, down, down near Canal Street.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It's called [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Dunehoffer's. ?] And they hire women now.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went down there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I got a job for $12 a week.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "To me, that was a fortune.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
